[SHORT DESC]
Does damage equal to the user's level.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Does damage equal to the user's level. Can hit Ghost-types.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>This move is a tad weak, but it's useful to deal physical damage from Pokemon with a low Attack stat, such as Alakazam or Chansey, who will deal more damage to other Alakazam and Snorlax than using Psychic or other special coverage moves.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/night_shade">Night Shade</a> is a Ghost-type equivalent.</p>